        Like a superstar athlete who takes a hometown discount to keep a championship-contending team together, the leader and creator of Localeur Inc. has chosen to collect what amounts to an average annual salary of $32,400 since he launched the venture in 2013. Find out what drives him, and what he picks as his dream car.    







